\lim_{n\rightarrow\infty}{\ln{y_{n}}}=\lim_{v\rightarrow{0}}{v\ln{(1+x^{\frac{1}{v}})}}
\lim_{v\rightarrow{0}}{v}\cdot\lim_{v\rightarrow{0}}{\ln{(1+x^{\frac{1}{v}})}}
